<h2>Add a milestone</h2>

<p>Milestones help track key dates and deliverables in your project. To add a milestone:</p>

<ol>
    <li>Go to the project details page</li>
    <li>Click on the <strong>Milestones</strong> tab</li>
    <li>Click the <strong>Add milestone</strong> button</li>
    <li>Fill in the milestone details:
        <ul>
            <li>Title (required)</li>
            <li>Description (optional)</li>
            <li>Due date (required)</li>
            <li>Status (not started, in progress, on track, at risk, delayed, complete, or cancelled)</li>
            <li>Priority (optional)</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Click <strong>Create</strong> to save the milestone</li>
</ol>

<h3>Tips</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Use clear, descriptive titles for milestones</li>
    <li>Update milestone status regularly to reflect current progress</li>
    <li>Milestones can be edited or deleted if needed</li>
    <li>Completed milestones help track project progress over time</li>
</ul>

